headline: PPL to Gain From Steady Investment in Clean Energy & Infrastructure
summary: PPL advances its long-term infrastructure and clean-energy investments as it targets major emission cuts and carbon neutrality by 2050.

headline: XEL's Unit to Supply 200 MW Electric to Fermi's Project Matador Campus
summary: XEL secures a 200 MW power supply with Fermi America. The company is investing steadily to enhance its transmission & distribution capabilities.
